Comment: 10,0:00:22.37,0:00:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sybilladura Lelladybura. {shibiradyu-ra reradibyu-ra-}
Comment: 10,0:00:26.37,0:00:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When traditional and modern powers mingle,\Nthe gate to an unseen world will open.{## i had 5-6 better lines in place before realizing diana's reply renders them all moot}
Comment: 10,0:00:32.83,0:00:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Traditional and modern powers?
Comment: 10,0:00:37.83,0:00:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Comment: 10,0:00:41.34,0:00:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana, I believe that you can be the one to open that gate.
Comment: 10,0:00:47.13,0:00:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can create a new future for the Cavendish name.
Comment: 10,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Comment: 10,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving...
Comment: 10,0:02:39.32,0:02:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they still have some leftovers.
Comment: 10,0:02:52.72,0:02:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are absolutely certain that we cannot convince you to reconsider, Diana?
Comment: 10,0:02:59.06,0:03:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly grateful for the kindness you have shown me.
Comment: 10,0:03:02.63,0:03:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I have made my decision\Nafter thorough deliberation.
Comment: 10,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana's going to leave Luna Nova?!
Comment: 10,0:03:13.83,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She got a letter from home yesterday.
Comment: 10,0:03:18.59,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, when she read it, she suddenly said she'd return home to become the family head.
Comment: 10,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Comment: 10,0:03:25.89,0:03:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cavendish family has a lot going on...
Comment: 10,0:03:29.55,0:03:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been some awful rumors\Ngoing around, especially as of late.
Comment: 10,0:03:34.16,0:03:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean Diana has to {\fax-0.2}quit{\i0} school!
Comment: 10,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now's the only time she can!{## mouthflap soon}
Comment: 10,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh?
Comment: 10,0:03:41.03,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She says the ritual to pass the title down can only be held now,
Comment: 10,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and if she misses it, there won't be\Nanother chance for several years.
Comment: 10,0:03:47.60,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone expected her to inherit that position eventually...
Comment: 10,0:03:52.91,0:03:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think she wouldn't even get to graduate first...
Comment: 10,0:03:56.16,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And we just heard...
Comment: 10,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That late tonight...
Comment: 10,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to leave Luna Nova!
Comment: 10,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Today?
Comment: 10,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Comment: 10,0:04:12.17,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko?
Comment: 10,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana... Diana said...
Comment: 10,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That she's going to quit school!
Comment: 10,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Comment: 10,0:04:21.90,0:04:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The Cavendish family has been\Nfacing issues for quite some time now.
Comment: 10,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the teachers tried to stop her, right?
Comment: 10,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We did, but...
Comment: 10,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana's not really going to leave, right?
Comment: 10,0:04:38.12,0:04:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't happen.
Comment: 10,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Comment: 10,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko's late.
Comment: 10,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably getting chewed out by Finneran again.
Comment: 10,0:04:52.37,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that her?
Comment: 10,0:04:57.94,0:04:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
