Comment: 10,0:05:31.51,0:05:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your family's having some trouble, but does that really mean you need to go back yourself?
Comment: 10,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let your parents handle it.
Comment: 10,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for {\fax-0.2}you{\i0} to quit!
Comment: 10,0:05:41.54,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be too late even if you wait\Nuntil your school years are over.
