Comment: 10,0:05:54.47,0:06:00.29,Default,,15,15,0,,Those who depart Luna Nova are to do so secretly, \Nin the dead of night. That is our custom. {I think this is supposed to match when Diana did that prediction for Akko leaving school}{fine, I'll be the one to check}
Comment: 10,0:06:00.75,0:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even speaking to you like this is against the rules.
Comment: 10,0:06:04.75,0:06:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you understand, withdraw at once!
Comment: 10,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about customs?!
Comment: 10,0:06:09.78,0:06:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, {\fax-0.2}I{\i0} won't accept you just up and leaving!
Comment: 10,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I had almost forgotten your disposition.
Comment: 10,0:06:17.72,0:06:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This attitude of yours, the disdain you display\Nfor tradition and history, truly infuriates me.
Comment: 10,0:06:24.63,0:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I do not recall requiring your permission to drop out.
Comment: 10,0:06:29.07,0:06:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't just sit idly by while my rival's running away.
Comment: 10,0:06:33.07,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never once viewed you as my rival.
Comment: 10,0:06:38.68,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have vented to your satisfaction—
Comment: 10,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really what you want, Diana?
Comment: 10,0:06:44.21,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, coming to Luna Nova\Nhas always been my dream.
Comment: 10,0:06:48.29,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I idolized Chariot, so it was my dream to go to the same school as her.
Comment: 10,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, that dream has grown.
Comment: 10,0:06:55.42,0:07:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I experienced and all the people I met here are important to me.
Comment: 10,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I love everything here just as much as I love Chariot!
Comment: 10,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you love Luna Nova too, Diana?
Comment: 10,0:07:08.23,0:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really throw it all away so easily?
Comment: 10,0:07:11.05,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a house of learning. Everyone must leave the nest eventually.
Comment: 10,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My time simply came sooner.
