Comment: 10,0:07:21.74,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is my duty to protect it.
Comment: 10,0:07:25.67,0:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But why do {\fax-0.2}you{\i0} have to go so far?!
