Comment: 10,0:13:25.66,0:13:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am honestly ashamed that a silly ball game would turn into this uproar.
Comment: 10,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single one of them is a mindless buffoon.
Comment: 10,0:13:33.39,0:13:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Comment: 10,0:13:34.84,0:13:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you and your dad going to Diana's house?
Comment: 10,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We were invited.
Comment: 10,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they have something to show us.
Comment: 10,0:13:43.06,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you two are related.
Comment: 10,0:13:45.47,0:13:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That we are.
Comment: 10,0:13:46.66,0:13:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what brings you all the way out to the Cavendish estate?
Comment: 10,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to bring Diana back!
Comment: 10,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that... {Trigger: "Hey, don't forget Diana's a bamf"}{## this is also very much a scottish highlands getup. wedinburgh it is}
Comment: 10,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for honoring us with your visit!
Comment: 10,0:14:07.67,0:14:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been awaiting you, Lord Hanbridge. {please check both of those names. also, I wasn't aware Diana was Cinderella}{## hanbridge-hakushaku --> earl of hanbridge, as a title of british peerage; hanbridge-sama --> lord hanbridge, as an address}
Comment: 10,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be exhausted after your long journey.
Comment: 10,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come inside.
Comment: 10,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so truly grateful that you've come.
Comment: 10,0:14:30.34,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister of State Paul Hanbridge,\Nas well as the ever-handsome Andrew! {smug mofo}
Comment: 10,0:14:37.67,0:14:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who might this be?
Comment: 10,0:14:38.82,0:14:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, my name is Kagari Atsuko.
Comment: 10,0:14:42.33,0:14:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Comment: 10,0:14:46.16,0:14:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My, is she a friend of yours?
Comment: 10,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Comment: 10,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't accepted it!
Comment: 10,0:14:52.27,0:14:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does it matter whether you have or not?!
Comment: 10,0:14:55.13,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you must be touched in the head.
Comment: 10,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And would {\fax-0.2}you{\i0} care to explain\Nwhy you've arrived together?
Comment: 10,0:15:01.81,0:15:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why hello, Diana. We just happened to pick her up off the side of the road.
Comment: 10,0:15:08.38,0:15:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Carter, lead them inside.
Comment: 10,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Comment: 10,0:15:13.51,0:15:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Comment: 10,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Comment: 10,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Comment: 10,0:15:21.02,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you one of Diana's friends? I'm not well acquainted with the lineages of Oriental witches.
Comment: 10,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not from a witch lineage. {she's so cute and clueless and proud}
Comment: 10,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 10,0:15:30.32,0:15:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She does indeed feel like a poor imitation of a witch, doesn't she?
Comment: 10,0:15:34.09,0:15:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how the mighty Luna Nova has fallen.
Comment: 10,0:15:36.13,0:15:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she one of Diana's fans? {or follower, whatever}{## groupies isn't good}
Comment: 10,0:15:37.90,0:15:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she's come in an attempt to worm her way into the Cavendish family.
Comment: 10,0:15:41.39,0:15:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, she is no more than an uninvited guest.
Comment: 10,0:15:44.39,0:15:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you can find the door on your own.
Comment: 10,0:15:46.99,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that—
Comment: 10,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She is as much of a witch as I am!
Comment: 10,0:15:49.85,0:15:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not tolerate such a disrespectful tone towards my guest.
Comment: 10,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Comment: 10,0:15:54.78,0:15:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hang on, Diana!
Comment: 10,0:15:57.02,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pulling my arm off!
Comment: 10,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana, stop!
Comment: 10,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with their egotistic attitude?
Comment: 10,0:16:05.66,0:16:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like three times as bad as you! Besides—{## is that okay? saying that diana is "bad"?}{from context it matches egotistic}
Comment: 10,0:16:09.08,0:16:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:16:11.04,0:16:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sending you home first thing tomorrow morning.
Comment: 10,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep quiet until then.
Comment: 10,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you've got a nice mansion here!
Comment: 10,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Comment: 10,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?!
Comment: 10,0:16:20.34,0:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to the Young Lady's request.
Comment: 10,0:16:22.72,0:16:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Comment: 10,0:16:27.31,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Comment: 10,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is anguishing me.
Comment: 10,0:16:30.67,0:16:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We did not diligently store this dress away only to lay it out again for some girl from who knows where.
Comment: 10,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I can hear everything you're saying.
Comment: 10,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am saying it for you to hear me.
Comment: 10,0:16:42.07,0:16:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not mind, Anna.
Comment: 10,0:16:44.14,0:16:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother prepared this dress specially for your eleventh birthday.
Comment: 10,0:16:48.70,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleventh?!
Comment: 10,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can no longer wear it even if I wanted to.
Comment: 10,0:16:52.93,0:16:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And who knows what Aunt would say had she remained in that dirty uniform.
Comment: 10,0:16:57.39,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be the case...
Comment: 10,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it go, Anna.
Comment: 10,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside...
Comment: 10,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Diana's room?
Comment: 10,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's basically what I expected...
Comment: 10,0:17:08.94,0:17:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, except for that.
Comment: 10,0:17:11.48,0:17:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana, did you use to have a soft spot for cutesy stuff?
Comment: 10,0:17:15.61,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that!
Comment: 10,0:17:17.81,0:17:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Comment: 10,0:17:23.31,0:17:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head out first. Anna, please take care of the rest.
Comment: 10,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Comment: 10,0:17:46.39,0:17:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, I've never met a witch so undeserving of care before.
Comment: 10,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really a student of Luna Nova?
Comment: 10,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone if I annoy you so much.
Comment: 10,0:17:55.32,0:17:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is out of the question. The Young\NLady has tasked me with this job.
Comment: 10,0:17:59.54,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Goody me, is that so? {Akko's being expectedly facetious}
Comment: 10,0:18:03.07,0:18:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The motto of the Cavendish family is "Affection".\NBe grateful for the Young Lady's kindheartedness.
Comment: 10,0:18:07.78,0:18:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindhearted? Diana? You must be jesting.
Comment: 10,0:18:12.43,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can assure you that the Young Lady\Nis kind. She takes after her mother.
Comment: 10,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana's mom?
Comment: 10,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana's becoming the family head.
Comment: 10,0:18:21.46,0:18:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, that means...
Comment: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Phải không?
Comment: 10,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She lost her parents at a tender age.
Comment: 10,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know...
Comment: 10,0:18:32.08,0:18:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said all sorts of things to her...
Comment: 10,0:18:35.38,0:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to take the Young Lady back to Luna Nova?
Comment: 10,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Comment: 10,0:18:39.65,0:18:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm afraid you will have to give up on that. If the\NYoung Lady does not become the family head now,
Comment: 10,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the House of Cavendish will perish!
Comment: 10,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That couldn't possibly—
Comment: 10,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It can, and it will!
Comment: 10,0:18:50.34,0:18:56.74,Default,,15,15,0,,If Madam Daryl, the proxy head, continues to do as she wishes, the scant remainder of our assets will vanish! {I figured she's too old to be a Lady? or you can do that}
Comment: 10,0:18:56.74,0:19:02.30,Default,,15,15,0,,The Young Lady must take her place as the rightful heir and return the family to its former glory as the new head!
Comment: 10,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that woman really so horrible?
Comment: 10,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers to a splendid night!
Comment: 10,0:19:10.10,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers to a splendid night.
Comment: 10,0:19:37.58,0:19:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, Daryl. I presume there was a reason you invited me to the manor.
Comment: 10,0:19:43.53,0:19:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You are correct, Paul. That will expedite the process.
Comment: 10,0:19:49.12,0:19:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain there will be at least\None thing to catch your fancy.
Comment: 10,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,These are?
Comment: 10,0:19:57.27,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Various items that I would appreciate you purchasing, rather than anyone else.
Comment: 10,0:20:05.41,0:20:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a candle holder made from the scales of the seventh Cavendish head's favorite mermaid.{## that is brutal}
Comment: 10,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a mythril chess set. {hm, apparently it's mithril in tolkein. which do you think looks nicer?}{## the final fantasy one...}
Comment: 10,0:20:22.08,0:20:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally:{## yo were you trying to fuck with me}{fuckin ho speaks over the keyframe, if she didn't I'd keep this}
Comment: 10,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tapestry of Beatrix!
Comment: 10,0:20:32.76,0:20:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh—
Comment: 10,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrix?
Comment: 10,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The inheritance of the first Cavendish witch,
Comment: 10,0:20:39.95,0:20:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,none other than one of the Nine Olde Witches, Beatrix the Affectionate!
Comment: 10,0:20:43.90,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 10,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana is descended from one of the Nine Olde Witches?!
Comment: 10,0:20:47.98,0:20:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine Olde Witches? Is that really worth getting so surprised over?
Comment: 10,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You must forgive me, as I cannot grasp the value this holds.
Comment: 10,0:20:56.63,0:21:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is all you wanted, I see no reason to overstay my welcome.
Comment: 10,0:21:00.39,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Comment: 10,0:21:01.84,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul, please, couldn't you take at least one?
Comment: 10,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, Andrew, didn't any catch your interest?
Comment: 10,0:21:07.00,0:21:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll give you a discount!
Comment: 10,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Comment: 10,0:21:10.68,0:21:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How much more must you trample over the\NCavendish history until you are satisfied?!
Comment: 10,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again.
Comment: 10,0:21:17.64,0:21:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your obsession with the old working out for you?
Comment: 10,0:21:21.09,0:21:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister spent all her time helping others for free because of those traditions. {nee-san i.e. older sister, but because Diana's mom was the head it's implied}{## why is "helping" in quotation marks? i don't get this line, reads weird}{fine, I was trying to emphasize it. the important part was how to phrase "for free" though}
Comment: 10,0:21:24.75,0:21:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And how did that turn out for your mother?! {fucking harsh, lady}
Comment: 10,0:21:27.40,0:21:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason our house has continued to hold out this long is because of all the work {\fax-0.2}I'm{\i0} doing.
Comment: 10,0:21:33.86,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All you've done is sell off the priceless and precious things that our ancestors left us for money!
Comment: 10,0:21:39.61,0:21:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you no pride as a Cavendish?!
Comment: 10,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can your "pride" put food on the table?
Comment: 10,0:21:46.49,0:21:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are your mother's daughter in that regard.
Comment: 10,0:21:49.83,0:21:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The age where magic reigned supreme has ended.
Comment: 10,0:21:53.08,0:21:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, will have to accept this reality in due time.
Comment: 10,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I am fully aware of your intentions, Aunt.
Comment: 10,0:22:02.27,0:22:04.98,Default,,15,15,0,,As I suspected, I can no longer leave this house in your hands.
Comment: 10,0:22:05.48,0:22:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's why you returned in such a rush.
Comment: 10,0:22:09.86,0:22:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Comment: 10,0:22:11.57,0:22:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the ritual to become the family head\Ncould only be held on a night when the stars align?
Comment: 10,0:22:15.86,0:22:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And tonight is that very night, coming just once every several years.
Comment: 10,0:22:20.09,0:22:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 10,0:22:23.02,0:22:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, I shall conduct the ritual in the shrine, and once and for all...
Comment: 10,0:22:27.04,0:22:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Become the Cavendish family head!
Comment: 10,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.66,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,Lady...
Comment: 10,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.66,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,Young Lady...
Comment: 10,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.97,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't want to admit it, but it's a perfect fit.
